com.codebox.bean

Class JavaBeanTester

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codebox.bean.JavaBeanTester

  • public final class JavaBeanTester
extends Object
    This helper class can be used to unit test the get/set/equals/canEqual/toString/hashCode methods of JavaBean-style Value Objects.
    Author:
    rob.dawson, jeremy.landis

public static final boolean PERFORM_CAN_EQUALS

        Tests the equals/hashCode/toString methods of the specified class.

        E - the type parameter associated with the extension class under test.
        Parameters:
        clazz - the class under test.
        extension - extension of class under test.
        loadData - load underlying data with values.
        Throws:
        IntrospectionException - thrown if the JavaBeanTester.load method throws this exception for the class under test.
        InstantiationException - thrown if the clazz.newInstance() method throws this exception for the class under test.
        IllegalAccessException - thrown if the clazz.newIntances() method throws this exception for the class under test.

        builder(Class), JavaBeanTesterBuilder.testObjectMethods()

        @Deprecated
public static <T> void equalsTests(T instance,
                              T expected,
                              boolean loadData)
                        throws IntrospectionException
        Deprecated. in favor of builder method.
        Equals Tests will traverse one object changing values until all have been tested against another object. This is done to effectively test all paths through equals.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type parameter associated with the class under test.
        Parameters:
        instance - the class instance under test.
        expected - the instance expected for tests.
        loadData - load underlying data with values.
        Throws:
        IntrospectionException - thrown if the Introspector.getBeanInfo() method throws this exception for the class under test.
        See Also:
        builder(Class), JavaBeanTesterBuilder.testEquals(Object, Object)

        Tests the get/set/equals/hashCode/toString methods of the specified class.
        Type Parameters:

        E - the type parameter associated with the extension class under test.

        clazz - the class under test.
        extension - extension of class under test.
